token_lists.title: The First Rain
token_lists.description:
Five. 
It were only five of them. 
Five Valkyries.
Only five.

Nobody could believe it.
But it is true.
There were only five Valkyries who destroyed the last remaining enemies.
Only five who saved the unsiverse.

Every single member of them has their own special power:
Belcoo is a born leader. She is kind, she is generous, she is smart. And she trusts her crew - no matter what! She knows how to bring the absolute best out of all of them.
Fang is the right hand of Belcoo and the strategist of the crew. He has the ability to plan at least 5 steps ahead.
Tunosode is the youngest of the crew but also the strongest! If you'll ever fight against her then I'm truly sorry for you! But nevertheless she's always fighting fair and she only fights to protect what and who is important to her. But when she's fighting then with all her power!
Susyma is the oldest of the crew. Susyma has the knowledge of thousands of years and Susyma knows how to use it! But Susyma never would use it to harm people even if Susyma definitely would be able to. Susyma has a quite, supporting and strong personality - if you would ever need help Susyma would be there for you. No matter what.
And then there's Basil. Basil is the rebell of this stunning crew. She often disagrees with Belcoo but this isn't a bad thing at all. Because of this Belcoo has changed the plans sometimes - and it turned out that they were the best way to do it. Basil has a stormy personality and she spits her anger right in your face if she feels the need to. But she's is always honest - never disrespectful, just very energetic. She has a very own way to do things but this often leads to new perspectives and helped the crew to find their way out of some difficult situations.

Now that you know these things about the crew - can you now imagine that they were the ones who saved the universe?
Well I can. I mean.. look at them - don't they look like heroes? At least they're the perfect team and they'll always fight side by side, never leaving one behind.

This crew is called "The First Rain".
Because when they appear the clouds always break up and let it rain. It's healing rain which washes out all the bad that happened on the ground where "The First Rain" is fighting for justice.

token_lists.title: The Valkyrie
token_lists.description:
Five valkyries from different planets band together to form the most formidable force hunting down mischiefs, delinquents and even feared monsters across galaxies. 

There were no reports on how their victims suffer their fate once these bounty hunters track them. I guess it's not unusual given the fact that there are no survivors other than pieces of horns and bones used as masks or ornaments. 
Be quick and warn others! These chicks are not angels; they are savages!
